title: Light & bright |Large windows | 1BR apt | Walk-in closet | LUX kitchen
posting_body: ['Our spacious studios, one, two and three bedroom apartments are noticeably larger than neighboring apartment communities.', 'With a large air conditioned living room, private deck and ceiling fans, mirrored closet doors and built-in closet organizers in every bedroom, you’ll be living in comfort.', 'This apartment features:', 'Fully-equipped kitchen w/ built-in Microwave.', 'Hard-wood Flooring', 'Pets Welcome', 'Lovely breakfast bar and dining area', 'Convenient washer & dryer inside', 'Central Heat & Air-conditioned comfort', 'Generous closets', 'Controlled-access building', 'Come Visit us!', 'Park Terrace', '860 Quince Ave', 'Santa Clara, CA 95051', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Office Hours', 'Tuesday - Friday 9:00AM to 6:00PM', 'Saturday 9:00AM – 2:00PM', 'Closed Sunday & Monday', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: santa clara, hwy 280, lawrence expy, san tomas expy, kaiser, pets, santa clara unified school district, pomeroy elementary, cabrillo middle school, santa clara high school']
